name: Fix pointId int32→int64
requires: []

scope: |
  pointId in TrackPoint, TrackEvent, TrackPointInfo interfaces is currently
  typed as `number` (safe only to 2^53). The server uses int64.
  Options:
  - Use string type for pointId (safest, no precision loss)
  - Use custom JSON parser with BigInt for pointId fields
  Update all interfaces that contain pointId.

